se" aria-controls="replo-:R6avb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-h64zi4"><div data-rid="a858b128-bd4a-4218-a9a0-b30659bb6b62" class="r-105933h alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Product Description</p></span></div><div data-rid="cf9f1c4a-4c0a-446a-87f9-23bee644c25a" class="r-1718bl2" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1fvkv1u" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R6avb2:"><div data-rid="1d528e9f-fcbf-477b-852c-afd86c6b9556" class="r-j9ycdq"><div data-rid="dd263528-e14f-4c60-81bd-3a3139425940" class="r-1gz4dl7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Arccos Air is a compact wearable that clips to your belt or slides in your pocket. Built-in motion sensors and GPS detect every shot automatically, powered by AI trained on 1.5 billion+ real golf shots. No sensors on your clubs. No phone required. Just play your round while Arccos captures everything in the background.</p><p><br></p><p>Your purchase includes the Arccos Air wearable, a charging case, and one year of Arccos Game Tracking Membership with full access to the Arccos app, including Strokes Gained Analytics, Smart Club Distances, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and more.</p><p><br></p><p>Compatible with iOS, Android coming soon. Works with or without Smart Sensors.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="a5929277-7c6f-43eb-a5eb-0176b248e3ad" class="r-31f9tg" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="d7c71306-2923-4dfa-bdb9-aaa4e5e7202b" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Raavb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1sbyhgt"><div data-rid="a571eb63-f74c-4c75-a112-