><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Reavb2:"><div data-rid="cf94d893-9242-49dd-b0c8-6581e9091b1e" class="r-aeenbk"><div data-rid="7c11ebb3-0b36-462f-b990-6ea7d8ffb2f0" class="r-1uho6ld alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No, that's now optional. Arccos Air tracks your game automatically without any sensors on your clubs. Every shot is detected by the wearable. Just play. You get full access to Strokes Gained, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and scoring insights. For the deepest club-level insights, many members prefer to also use Smart Sensors — but they're completely optional.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="016c4891-8371-4ac2-9f66-b90e5649ad8c" class="r-1hx3iss" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="86ad1954-10e1-4c11-b835-5038f2d7cd1f" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Riavb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-u4dnsq"><div data-rid="480ca129-9745-4f7d-baf9-48e3166b324b" class="r-id5qbm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Do I need to carry my phone?</p></span></div><div data-rid="c8d5c995-54a9-4f2c-b712-62d368d7453f" class="r-1c3n1" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1whbqdd" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Riavb2:"><div data-rid="b90cfa8c-b891-4db9-99ae-e9e5529bd994" class="r-1lh3lgj"><div data-rid="ad075d3d-b510-4faa-ad00-02518c654436" class="r-94786a alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No. That's one of the biggest differences with Arccos Air. The wearable replaces the need for your phone or an Apple Watch on the course. Just slip Air in your pocket, or clip it on your belt and play. Your shot data syncs to the app after your round or whenever you're back in range.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="a6817717-7948-4c8c-9b66-42aba2d13f69" class="r-1pede7q" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="4b35aca6-1f94-4cfd-a99c-16670b99a00e" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rmavb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1fhd5va"><div data-rid="8cf35fdd-3b4a-426e-b913-f7a7f825da9d" class="r-ftz8k alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How accurate is the shot tracking?</p></span></div><div data-rid="e54d919e-14a0-4a25-acc6-92bbd8625c12" class="r-x3kjz3" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-h7l6hs" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rmavb2:"><div data-rid="69ea178f-7413-4758-8022-0be94e724dd7" class="r-1nyhr16"><div data-rid="dde05940-3452-4788-b9ef-432c90f6c4f9" class="r-13kpv6h alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Arccos Air detects shots with a high degree of accuracy from your very first round — and it gets better as you play. The AI is trained on 1.5 billion+ real golf shots from golfers at every level and trusted by PGA TOUR professionals. If a shot is occasionally missed or added, minor edits in the app take seconds and give you insights you can trust.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c84ada57-29c4-477b-b8f2-83253f6ad16d" class="r-caewi5" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="a238c8bb-7b6f-4d0c-ba3e-adec867fa30e" class="r-1